                     <interp inst="t18290611-156-person1201" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             well knowing, &amp;c.: against the Statute, &amp;c.; and that he afterwards, on the said 14th day of January, at Chepping Wycomb aforesaid, one piece of counterfeited money, made to the likeness, &amp;c. of a shilling, as and for a good one, unlawfully, &amp;c. did utter, &amp;c. to Ann, the wife of 
               <persName id="t18290611-156-person1202">
                  Aaron 
                  Worster
